---
// Component Imports
import Page from "../layouts/Page.astro";
import Head from "../layouts/Head.astro";
import Hero from "../layouts/WorkHero.astro";
import ensys from "../images/ensys.png";
import ensysFull from "../images/ensys-lg.png";
import Modal from "../components/Modal.astro";
import ButtonIcon from "../components/ButtonIcon.astro";
import { Image, Picture } from "@astrojs/image/components";

const meta = {
  title: "Ensys Engineers",
  description: "Business website for a heat pump manufacturing business.",
};
---

<Page>
  <Head slot="head" {meta} />
  <Hero />
  <main
    id="content-wrapper"
    class="container mx-auto py-6 px-8 md:py-24 md:px-0 lg:py-12 dark:bg-dark-900 dark:text-white"
  >
    <div
      class="container min-h-full space-y-12 my-2 text-left leading-relaxed px-4 lg:px-8"
    >
      <div
        id="pagination"
        class="flex flex-wrap space-x-2 items-center bg-white rounded-1 shadow-md p-4"
      >
        <a
          href="/"
          class="hover:transition-all hover:ease hover:text-geraldine-500 hover:duration-200 focus:outline-none focus:border-b-4 focus:border-slate-500"
          tabindex="0">Home</a
        >
        <span class="h-6 w-6 i-mdi:chevron-double-right"></span>
        <a
          href="/work/#content-wrapper"
          class="hover:transition-all hover:ease hover:text-geraldine-500 hover:duration-200 focus:outline-none focus:border-b-4 focus:border-slate-500"
          tabindex="0">Work</a
        >
        <span class="h-6 w-6 i-mdi:chevron-double-right"></span>
        <a
          href="#"
          class="focus:outline-none focus:border-b-4 focus:border-slate-500"
          tabindex="0">Ensys Engineers</a
        >
      </div>

      <div class="font-display my-6 text-f-xl fw600" id="anchor">
        Ensys
        <span class="text-sky-600 dark:text-sky-300">Engineers</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col items-start md:flex-row">
        <div
          class="flex border-2 border-gray-200 flex-shrink-0 shadow-lg my-4 mx-2 md:w-1/2 lg:w-auto dark:border-gray-800 hover:border-geraldine-400 dark:hover:border-geraldine-400"
        >
          <Image
            class="h-auto object-contain w-full dark:filter dark:brightness-75 dark:contrast-125"
            src={ensys}
            alt="Ensys"
            width={480}
            height={270}
          />
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col space-y-4 my-4 px-2 md:pl-6">
          <p>
            This heat pump manufacturing business required a website to showcase
            the pumps they were making along with the manufacturing facilities,
            their past clients, and a contact page that showed their location on
            a map.
          </p>

          <p>This project's key points and requirements were as follows:</p>

          <ul class="list-inside list-decimal">
            <li>Local business website.</li>
            <li>Responsive design.</li>
            <li>Image slider.</li>
            <li>Contact form with map.</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="flex flex-items-start flex-wrap">
            <div class="p-2">
              <ButtonIcon
                href="http://ensys.in"
                target="_blank"
                color="bg-sky-700 hover:bg-sky-600 dark:bg-sky-400 dark:hover:bg-sky-500"
                iconClass="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-current i-bx-link-external"
              >
                Website
              </ButtonIcon>
            </div>
            <div class="p-2">
              <ButtonIcon
                id="modal2-trigger"
                color="bg-gray-100 border-1 border-gray-300 hover:bg-gray-200 text-gray-700 dark:bg-slate-400 dark:hover:bg-slate-500 cursor-pointer"
                iconClass="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-current i-icon-park-twotone:screenshot-one"
              >
                Screenshot
              </ButtonIcon>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="bg-white border rounded-md flex flex-col border-gray-200 shadow-md p-6 gap-4 justify-around sm:flex-row dark:bg-dark-700 dark:border-dark-600"
      >
        <div>
          <div
            class="rounded-full border-gray-300 border-2 w-28 h-28 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto md:ml-12 md:mb-8"
          >
            <span class="i-uim-user-md w-16 h-16"></span>
          </div>
          <span
            class="flex-shrink-0 h-10 text-geraldine-600 w-10 i-bxs-quote-alt-left md:h-12 md:w-12"
          ></span>

          <div class="space-y-3 px-4 md:px-8">
            <p>
              We thank Akshay for the fantastic job done for our website Ensys.
            </p>

            <p>
              It was a pleasure working with Akshay, as he worked closely with
              us at every step in developing the site. We value his creative
              input that exceeded our expectations.
            </p>

            <p>
              He is young but very professional, committed to focusing on the
              customerâ€™s needs and showing a genuine interest in helping the
              customer to achieve the required results. From the first moment we
              felt that our project was in good hands and that the experience,
              knowledge and enthusiasm of this young man would show in our new
              website.
            </p>

            <p class="text-right fw600">- Ensys Engineers</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-shrink-0 items-end place-content-end">
          <span
            class="h-10 text-geraldine-600 w-10 i-bxs-quote-alt-right md:h-12 md:w-12"
          ></span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Modal triggerId="modal2-trigger" title="Ensys Engineers">
    <div class="mt-3 grid place-content-center">
      <Picture
        class="dark:filter dark:brightness-75 dark:contrast-125"
        src={ensysFull}
        alt="Ensys Engineers Full Image"
        widths={[300, 450, 600]}
        sizes="(max-width: 768px) 300px, (max-width: 1024px) 450px, 600px"
        aspectRatio={1}
      />
    </div>
  </Modal>
</Page>
